				</div>
				<div class="group text-center">
					<div class="w-24 h-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500 to-emerald-600 rounded-3xl mx-auto mb-8 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 shadow-lg shadow-emerald-500/25">
						<svg class="w-12 h-12 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
